<p>In today's live lesson you wrote your own <code>safe_input</code> and applied it to your Pokédex. Explain <strong>the code you wrote</strong> in a short phone video. You may show it running with some bad input on purpose. Try to use: <strong>function</strong>, <strong>safe_input</strong>, <strong>log</strong>, <strong>append</strong>, <strong>report</strong>.</p>
